{"tid":1754053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印巴港人為少數族裔發聲","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6242030b35fa34a19a38d6d6ec1edf5874f4d14","tid":1754053,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/HOD2AHJ36IASNOJBYLWV2YN3H4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FHOD2AHJ36IASNOJBYLWV2YN3H4%2F&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=974880c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191125%2FHOD2AHJ36IASNOJBYLWV2YN3H4%2F&h=82e82ed6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191125/HOD2AHJ36IASNOJBYLWV2YN3H4/</a><br />\n<br />\n印巴港人為少數族裔發聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191125/large/1574612172_8cf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191125%2Flarge%2F1574612172_8cf0.jpg&h=210c36df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】離島區以東涌南選區的選戰最為激烈，多達四人爭取一個議席，票站昨日湧現人龍，在排隊選民中包括印巴港人Sam （圖）。<br />\n<br />\nSam表示，並不介意花時間排隊進入票站，強調投票是每一位港人應盡之責，亦是每名公民首要職責，即使高峯期有多達逾百人排隊，他會耐心等待至完成投票才離開。<br />\n<br />\nSam又表示，作為一名合格的當選區議員，必須關心社區議題，並且持續發展及改善現有社區設施及環境，為現存政府制度缺失補漏，才能對得起每名選民投下的一票，故此他希望以手上的選票，表達本港少數族裔的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎敬中"},{"pid":"18f95f01833fcf6dca8ffc57fdfab345b11e500b","tid":1754053,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot